寧靜<br />\r\n我既身心都得到解脫<br />\r\nMk仔mk妹好似走火警咁<br />\r\n唔係 用走火警都唔足以形容當時情況<br />\r\n應該用911黎形容先恰當<br />\r\n最後 <br />\r\n我要比多500蚊清潔費啲人先肯放我走<br />\r\n我發誓以後都唔食月餅！！！！"},{"pid":"90d0f60e47785fc6e9f1b9d287da1517f6698404","tid":768081,"uid":18200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:51:06.000Z","msg":"唱男女合唱<br />\n<br />\n無女同你唱 唱女個part要伴唱<br />\n<br />\n好柒啊"},{"pid":"90f432c9e17f0f7cdcb50b42e8e291a89ea54c12","tid":768081,"uid":28759,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:52:01.000Z","msg":"最撚憎係啲吸毒廣告<br />\n可唔可以簽張紙話我唔吸毒<br />\n以後唔播俾我<br />\n<br />\n大佬你啲廣告錯撚晒 target <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae11295494d24a4c486d4e278dae757a1ba2c24","tid":768081,"uid":46854,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"禁忌係乜柒香港歌都唔識走黎唱K<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時淨係聽埋哂啲大陸歌<br />\n去到neway red mr冇你啲大陸歌又要話「吓~~咁都冇~~大陸又平又多歌啦~~」<br />\n人地唱万刀甲屎塔肥又要話人mk<br />\n咁你自己慢慢返你嘅大陸唱唔好係我香港K房嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81764b6a29237285ebe3d4051b3be25bcbfc28ee","tid":768081,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4cc0e217176b7afbb7a44cb01fa389ad4bb9044a","tid":768081,"uid":143116,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T01:32:51.000Z","msg":"唱D首歌好熱鬧但係在場冇人識嘅歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過同fd唱k佢點AKB48嘅high tension，首歌好high好熱鬧但係在場得佢一個識呢首歌，間房靜曬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:53:28.000Z","msg":"得罪你咩家陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614750ad318424fd90409758782816f8c30da527","tid":768081,"uid":135866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dd0dd287d9ca4f58807bd2dc93dd12b8e16f8bf","tid":768081,"uid":26102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-0